The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | The City Diary
                                                                                                               The City Diary
                Entry of visitors to the domestic and international terminals of Netaji Subhas Chandra Bose International Airport was prohibited from Tuesday night to August 20. A senior airport official said the ban was part of the security measures for Independence Day.     Cyclists Hasan Gafir and Sheikh Shameem were critically injured after a car lost control near Kestopur on VIP Road and hit them. The two were admitted to RG Kar Medical College with serious hand, shoulder and pelvic injuries. The cops intercepted the vehicle and detained the driver.     Homemaker Rimu Barui, 30, was found hanging from the ceiling of her room in her Tarak Paramanik Road home, near Girish Park, on Tuesday afternoon. Rimu had been suffering from depression after fighting with her husband Chandrasekhar, a hawker, over their only sons education, said police. The couple married 10 years ago. Their son studies in Class III in a local school. Chandrasekhar spotted Rimu hanging from the ceiling around 1pm. The body has been sent for post-mortem.    Pasupati Patra, a 75-year-old resident of Basudebbati in Sankrail, Howrah, died after an unknown vehicle hit him on NH6 near Ranihati on Tuesday morning. Police said local residents and shopkeepers found Patra lying in a pool of blood and rushed him to Howrah district hospital, where he died.     Jyoti Mandal, 16, and Susmita Mandal, 12 were injured after a portion of a dilapidated boundary wall fell on them in Mallipanchghara, Howrah, on Tuesday evening. Jyoti and Susmita were walking along the boundary wall when it collapsed on them around 6.30pm, said police. The two were admitted to a nursing home. Residents extricated them from under the debris.                                                                                                                                                                    
